IN RE the MARRIAGE OF Deborah WHITFORD and Richard Whitford Upon the Petition of Deborah Whitford, Petitioner-Appellee, And Concerning Richard Whitford, Respondent-Appellant. No. 17-2081 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed December 5, 2018

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

Richard Whitford appeals the district court's dismissal of his petition to modify the parties' dissolution decree. AFFIRMED.

AFFIRMED.
